<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
<locus from="3r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT1716Kidanz">Morning prayer</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ኪዳን፡ ዘነግህ፡ ዘተናገረ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ትንሣኤሁ፡ እሙታን። በረከቱ፡ ወሀብተ፡ ረድኤቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ዮሐንስ፡
ወምስለ፡ ንግሥትነ፡ ሰብለ፡ ወንጌል፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ይብል፡ ካህን፡ ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅ'፡ ኃያል፡ ቅ'፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡</incipit>
<textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
<locus from="5v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT1717Kidanz">Evening prayer</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ኪዳን፡ ዘሰርክ፡ ይብል፡ ካህን። ጸጋሁ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለክሙ።</incipit>
<textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.3">
<locus from="6v"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT4711Mastabqwe">Various intercessory prayers: for the sick, travellers,
rain, the fruits of the earth, the waters of the rivers, the regnant king (<persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne">John</persName>), the dead,
children, and the peace of the Church.</title>
<note>The note on the margin: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝኒ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘሐዋርያት፡ ዘተሠርዐ፡ በሲኖዶስ፡</foreign></note>
<textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.4">
<locus from="10r"/>
<title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="LIT4346Prayer">ሊጦን፡ or <foreign xml:lang="grc">Λιτανεία</foreign></title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ወካዕበ፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅዝ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ለእግዚአ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። እንዘ፡ ነአኵቶ፡ እስመ፡ ዓቀበነ፡ በኑኀ፡
ሌሊት፡ ወአብጽሐነ፡ እምጽልመት።</incipit>
<note>The note on the margin: ዝኒ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘሊቃውንት።</note>
<textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
</msItem>

